casebody.data:
Mahoning County Bar Association v. Strobel.

[Cite as Mahoning Cty. Bar. Assn. v. Strobel (1989), 41 Ohio St. 3d 611.]

(No. D.D. 88-34 Submitted February 14, 1989 Decided March 15, 1989.)

Albert Strobel is publicly reprimanded.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
